The name of the project is ‘Bank Loan Default Prediction’ where the primary focus of the project is to determine various factors that can help in predicting the loan whether will be defaulted by a customer. 
This will help the bank in taking corrective measures before sanctioning loan basis the applicant profile information wherein the bank can deny a loan to customer who is highly likely to default and approve loan to those set of customers that are more likely to repay the loan on time thus avoiding business loss.  

